OL,3,CMore than 1,000 prisoners to be freed
OL,4,Cin second round of early releases
OL,6,FAnother 1,100 prisoners are due to be
OL,7,Freleased early next week as the
OL,8,FGovernment continues to battle with
OL,9,Fjail overcrowding.
OL,11,FThe prisoners form the second round of
OL,12,Fearly releases under a policy
OL,13,Fintroduced early in the Government's
OL,14,Fterm to reduce the proportion of a
OL,15,Fsentence most offenders must serve
OL,16,Fbehind bars from 50% to 40%.
OL,18,FThe first round of releases, in mid-
OL,19,FSeptember, saw 1,700 inmates set free
OL,20,Fearly and helped the prison population
OL,21,Ffall from a record of 88,521 to 86,333.
