OL,3,CMore than 1,000 prisoners to be freed
OL,4,Cin second round of early releases
OL,6,FNumbers have since risen again,
OL,7,Freaching 87,028 on Friday, just below
OL,8,Fthe levels seen when Justice Secretary
OL,9,FShabana Mahmood announced the plans in
OL,10,FJuly.
OL,12,FMs Mahmood had warned then that
OL,13,Fprisons risked running out of space,
OL,14,Fpotentially causing the collapse of
OL,15,Fthe justice system as courts would
OL,16,Fhave nowhere to send convicted
OL,17,Fcriminals.
