OL,3,CMore than 1,000 prisoners to be freed
OL,4,Cin second round of early releases
OL,6,FThe early release scheme does not
OL,7,Fapply to some inmates, including those
OL,8,Fconvicted of sexual, domestic abuse or
OL,9,Fterrorism offences, or violent
OL,10,Foffenders serving sentences of more
OL,11,Fthan four years.
OL,13,FSeptember saw 37 inmates released in
OL,14,Ferror after their sentences had not
OL,15,Fbeen correctly logged. Ms Mahmood
OL,16,Fconfirmed on Thursday that all 37 were
OL,17,Fback in custody.
