OL,3,CMore than 1,000 prisoners to be freed
OL,4,Cin second round of early releases
OL,6,FMs Mahmood is expected to launch a
OL,7,Freview of sentencing during the week,
OL,8,Fwhich is likely to consider several
OL,9,Freforms including whether tougher
OL,10,Fcommunity sentences would be more
OL,11,Feffective than short spells in prison.
OL,13,FThis follows her announcement that
OL,14,Fmagistrates' sentencing powers will be
OL,15,Fdoubled again, allowing them to jail
OL,16,Fcriminals for up to a year.
