OL,3,CMore than 1,000 prisoners to be freed
OL,4,Cin second round of early releases
OL,6,FThe move is intended to ease the
OL,7,Fbacklog in the crown courts and reduce
OL,8,Fthe number of remand prisoners waiting
OL,9,Fto receive sentences, but the Justice
OL,10,FSecretary acknowledged this would
OL,11,Finitially "see a slight increase in
OL,12,Fthe overall prison population".
OL,14,FBut the Criminal Bar Association
OL,15,Fwarned that extending magistrates'
OL,16,Fpowers was a "short-term and long-term
OL,17,Fbackfire" as it could "sharply
OL,18,Fincrease" the overall prison
OL,19,Fpopulation within a matter of months.
